overview:
We have search the four corners of the Internet and have found tonnes of ebooks for you to download and start reading instantly all in one place.

We opened our doors early 2011 and currently already have a large amount of ebooks to offer.

We will be adding new titles constantly, therefore a steady flow of new ebooks daily.

Overtime we are hoping to be the largest free ebook distribution online without having to pay for a membership and non fiction ebooks with resale rights and fiction ebooks under the creative commons license.

Free Eboooks is maintained by Idolised Media which also maintains and operates Ebook Head which is our major partner site.

With most of our ebooks in the format pdf you will have the option to read on your electronic device such as your iPad, Kindle, ebook readers etc…

We have thousands of free ebooks for you to download and start reading instantly… Remember, We have a passion for ebooks and everything electronic reading so if this sounds like you, you have found the right place…
